name: Faded Memories [Part Seven]
description:
About this series // I start my NFT journey with this genesis piece. This series tells the story of my photography genesis, as this feels right to me. These animated images tell the story of my first exploration adventure, revisiting the now-abandoned theme park I used to love as a child.

Part 7 of 7 // The final shots of the day are of the rollercoaster and one of the faux castles. The explore only took a few hours, the park was much smaller than I remembered. The state of abandonment of my childhood paradise left me quite sad. Although this was the start of my life exploring the abandoned world, and I am glad that my first place was here.

Mp4 | 1080x1080 pixels| July  2021
